n_{d}=\frac{N_{d}}{1+\frac{1}{g} \exp \left(\frac{E_{D}-E_{F}}{k T}\right)}
$ and $n_{d}=N_{d}-N_{d}^{+}$where $N_{d}^{+}$is ionized donor atoms concentration. according to question $
\begin{aligned}
n_{d} & =5 \% \text { of } N_{d} \\
g & =2 \text { degeneracy factor }
\end{aligned}
$ $
